<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../stylesheets/index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../stylesheets/fontello.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/edit_profile.js"></script>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>sign_up</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header style="padding-top: 10px;">
        <div id="header_up">
            <a class="h_ups" id="home_icon" href="/">&#xe800</a>
            <h1 class="h_ups" id="main_title"><a href="/" style="color: cornflowerblue;">D2VTS</a></h1>
           
            <div class="h_ups" id=login_div>
                
              <a href="/login" class="loginbtns" id="login_btn">&nbsp;로그인&nbsp;</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </header>
    <!-- 공백사용금지 :   <input type="text" name="test" id="test" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this);" onchange="noSpaceForm(this);" /> -->
        <div class="sign_up_form">
        <form action="/user2/update_process/" method="POST" onsubmit="return submitCheck()">

            
                <input id="this_is_edit" type="hidden" value="edit"/>
            

            <h2 id="sign_up_h1">회원정보수정</h2>
            <label>아이디</label>
            <p><input type = "id" name="id" id="id" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this)" required readonly value="<%=user_info.user_id%>">
            </p>
            <br id="id_form_check_br" />
            <p id="id_form_guide" style="display:none; color:red; font-size: 8px;">8~20자 영문대문자, 영문소문자, 숫자, 특수문자를 모두
                사용해야합니다.</p>

            <p>닉네임</p>
            <p><input type="text" name="nickname" id="nickname" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this)" required value="<%=user_info.nickname%>" ></p>
            <br id="nickname_form_check_br" />
            <p id="nickname_form_guide"></p>

            <p>전화번호( - 없이 입력)</p>
            <p><input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this)" required value="<%=user_info.phone%>" ></p>
            <br id="phone_form_check_br" />
            <p id="phone_form_guide"></p>

            <p>지역</p>
            <p><input type="text" id="area" name="area" required value="<%=user_info.area%>" ></p>
            <br id="area_form_check_br" />
            <p id="area_form_guide"></p>

            <br />
            
            <br />
            <input id="sign_up_submit" type="submit" onmousedown="checkall(this)" value="회원 정보 수정">
            </p>
        </form>

    </div>
    <div>

    </div>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0 auto;
            align-content: center;
        }

        #sign_up_h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .sign_up_form {
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 40%;
        }

        #sign_up_submit {
            background: rgb(0, 118, 255);
            color: white;
            width: 173px;
            height: 50px;
            font-size: 20px;
            border-radius: 7px 7px 7px 7px;
        }
    </style>
</body>

</html>